{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be clean and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artist Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #2c3e50;\n            --secondary-color: #34495e;\n            --accent-color: #bdc3c7;\n            --text-color: #ecf0f1;\n            --background-color: #2c3e50;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 0.5rem 0;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        #about {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        #about h2 {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        #portfolio .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .gallery-item .caption {\n            padding: 1rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        #contact {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            padding-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        #contact p {\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        #contact a {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact a:hover {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>[Artist Name]</h1>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#portfolio\">Portfolio</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>About Me</h2>\n        <p>Welcome to my portfolio! I am a local artist specializing in [mention your art style, e.g., abstract paintings, digital illustrations, sculptures]. My work explores themes of [mention themes, e.g., nature, urban life, human emotion].</p>\n        <p>I find inspiration in the vibrant community and unique landscapes of our city, translating these observations into visual narratives.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"portfolio\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Portfolio</h2>\n        <div class=\"gallery\">\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2c3e50/ffffff?text=Artwork+1\" alt=\"Artwork 1\">\n                <div class=\"caption\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 1</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the piece.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/34495e/ffffff?text=Artwork+2\" alt=\"Artwork 2\">\n                <div class=\"caption\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 2</h3>\n                    <p>Another descriptive sentence about this artwork.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2c3e50/ffffff?text=Artwork+3\" alt=\"Artwork 3\">\n                <div class=\"caption\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 3</h3>\n                    <p>Details on the medium and inspiration.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/34495e/ffffff?text=Artwork+4\" alt=\"Artwork 4\">\n                <div class=\"caption\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 4</h3>\n                    <p>Insights into the creative process.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Contact</h2>\n        <p>Interested in a commission or purchasing a piece? Feel free to reach out!</p>\n        <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:your.email@example.com\">your.email@example.com</a></p>\n        <p>Follow me on: <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a></p>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 [Artist Name]. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}